        {
            "id": 6396807,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 碩禾(3691)大漲7.62%，報120元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>碩禾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3691:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3691\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3691-TW</a>)25日12:22股價上漲8.5元，報120.0元，漲幅7.62%，成交460張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>碩禾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3691:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3691\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3691-TW</a>)所屬產業為光電業，主要業務為太陽能導電漿。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌6.3%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.58%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-16 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+17 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-33 張</li> <li>融資增減：-5 張</li> <li>融券增減：+6 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6396807",
